-------------------
  LCD Splash !
-------------------

Simple bash script which 'splashes' boot information to your
external LCDs :).

-------------------
  Caveats
-------------------

- written to work with baselayout 1.10.x and newer
- only tested with HPPA machines

-------------------
  Contact
-------------------

Please file bugs/requests/etc... over at
http://bugs.gentoo.org/

